.sp 3mm
:FED.
MasterCard on mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Virtual version of a physical private or Corporate card. Can be put into a
wallet approved by Handelsbanken, on a mobile unit such as a smartphone or
tablet.
After this, the virtual payment card on a mobile unit can be used as
contactless payment by means of a wallet when making physical purchases.
