Private liability
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You are solely and personally responsible for all payments, withdrawals
and other debits made using the card. Your liability also covers losses
attributable to unauthorised use of the card by others, although with
the limitations pursuant to Section 62 of the Danish Act on Payment
Services. See Article 2.9.
