:FED.
Corporate card - corporate liability
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A MasterCard Business Debit is used by the cardholder
to pay for expenses on behalf of his/her place of employment or company.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In principle, the company is liable for all claims concerning the
issuing and use of the card. In certain situations, the cardholder is
jointly and severally liable for claims regarding use of the card, see
Article 2.21.
